The Quadrilateral Security Dialogue (QSD), colloquially the Quad or QUAD, is a strategic security dialogue between Australia, India, Japan, and United States that is maintained by talks between member countries.

This dataset contains 600+ images of Each Quad Leaders [Narendra Modi, Joe Biden, Fumio Kishida, Scott Morrison ]
